Tga '''Tadrart''' yat tgrawt illan ɣ izzlmḍ n [[Agadir|ugadir]]. Twala i lqyadt n imuzzar ida utanan, nna iḍfarn tamnbaḍt n [[Tamnbaḍt n Agadir-Idawtanan|Agadir-Idawtanan]].

Ar gis ittuyskar yan ssuq kraygat ass n ssbt. D ar gis ittuyskar yan unmuggar kraygat anbdu ɣ wayyur n ɣuct.

